mpus%2C%20and%20became%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmad%20scientist%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20dorm%20room.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20make%20a%20powdery%20mess%20and%2C%20oftentimes%2C%20it%20was%20on%20top%20of%20a%20mini%20fridge%20%E2%80%94%20like%20in%20a%20bedroom%2C%20not%20even%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2029-year-old%20Williams%20College%20alum%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20taste%20%26quot%3Bleft%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Schrupp%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20didn't%20upset%20my%20stomach%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20mattered%20most%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20graduated%20in%202018%2C%20took%20a%20teaching%20position%20at%20a%20boarding%20school%20in%20New%20England%2C%20and%20moved%20onto%20a%20different%20campus%2C%20his%20protein%20powder%20equipment%20and%20ingredients%20in%20tow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lived%20in%20the%20dorm%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20privacy%20%E2%80%94%20as%20in%2C%20my%20life%20spilled%20over%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20my%20students%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20so%20they%20knew%20what%20I%20was%20up%20to%2C%20and%20they%20were%20very%20interested.%20At%20some%20point%20in%20time%2C%20we%20had%20a%20little%20tasting%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20was%20honestly%20very%20helpful%20feedback%20because%20they%20are%20brutally%20honest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchrupp%20continued%20tinkering%20with%20his%20recipe%2C%20testing%20variations%20with%20honey%2C%20date%20sugar%2C%20and%20maple%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22677ffe18-1b2c-4c1a-b27f-e4566475b275%5C%22%3EPartnering%20with%20a%20local%20bakery%20and%20spending%20%2420%2C000%20on%20his%20first%20round%20of%20inventory%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchrupp%20figured%20that%20other%20people%20with%20sensitive%20stomachs%20might%20be%20interested%20in%20his%20product.%20After%20years%20of%20experimentation%20and%20recipe%20refinement%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20test%20his%20hunch%20and%20launch%20a%20protein%20powder%20company%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drinkwholesome.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrink%20Wholesome%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20early%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20he%20did%20was%20cold%20call%20manufacturers%20and%20ask%20if%20they%20could%20make%20his%20product%20in%20bulk.%20He%20connected%20with%20a%20small%2C%20local%20granola%20company%20that%20did%20contract%20manufacturing%20for%20other%20local%20businesses%2C%20and%20they%20agreed%20to%20make%20his%20first%20batch%20in%20two%20flavors%3A%20mocha%20and%20peanut%20butter%20coconut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20hindsight%2C%20those%20are%20ridiculous%20flavors%20to%20launch%20with%20because%2C%20today%2C%2080%25%20of%20my%20sales%20are%20for%20vanilla%20and%20chocolate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%20%26quot%3BBut%20mocha%20and%20peanut%20butter%20were%20my%20favorite%20flavors.%20That's%20just%20what%20I%20liked%20the%20best%20and%20so%20that's%20what%20I%20started%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Schrupp%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d37da196626c40986070b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESchrupp%20graduated%20from%20Williams%20College%20in%202018.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jack%20Schrupp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20startup%20costs%20amounted%20to%20about%20%2420%2C000%2C%20which%20he%20pulled%20from%20his%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20make%20very%20much%20money%20teaching%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20very%20significant%20investment%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp%2C%20who%20had%20a%20loose%20sales%20plan%20of%20pitching%20his%20product%20to%20local%20grocery%20stores%20and%20setting%20up%20booths%20at%20local%20sporting%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20online%20was%20never%20on%20his%20radar%2C%20nor%20did%20he%20want%20it%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20forced%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fce0d5e-dcab-4060-b227-adcd59e555ca%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20the%202020%20pandemic%20'curveball'%20and%20the%202021%20bird%20flu%20outbreak%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchrupp%20received%20his%20first%20round%20of%20inventory%20in%20February%202020%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20outbreak%20shut%20much%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20sales%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pandemic%20really%20threw%20a%20curveball%20my%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Two%20months%20into%20lockdown%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20had%20not%20sold%20many%20bags%20at%20all%2C%20and%20I%20was%20genuinely%20convinced%20that%20I%20was%20just%20going%20to%20have%20to%20throw%20it%20all%20out%20and%20move%20on%20with%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20initially%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20setback%20turned%20into%20an%20advantage%3A%20His%20inability%20to%20meet%20with%20customers%20in%20person%20forced%20him%20to%20turn%20to%20online%20sales.%20He%20started%20selling%20on%20WooCommerce%20and%20Amazon%2C%20and%20while%20his%20initial%20customers%20were%20all%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20strangers%20eventually%20started%20finding%20his%20product.%20As%20of%202025%2C%2099%25%20of%20his%20sales%20come%20from%20those%20two%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20small-business%20owner%20who's%20never%20sought%20capital%20from%20investors%2C%20he's%20grown%20to%20appreciate%20e-commerce%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20not%20his%20ideal%20way%20of%20finding%20and%20interacting%20with%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20you%20to%20reach%20an%20incredibly%20large%20number%20of%20people%20with%20a%20small%2C%20finite%20amount%20of%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%20%26quot%3BE-commerce%20is%20incredible.%20What%20I%20will%20say%2C%20though%2C%20is%20it's%20not%20very%20rewarding.%20It's%20faceless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20faceless%20customers%20kept%20returning%2C%20though%2C%20eventually%20wiping%20out%20his%20initial%20inventory.%20He%20ordered%20a%20second%20round%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20he%20made%20vanilla%20and%20chocolate%20flavors%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202020.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20another%20unexpected%20event%20nearly%20put%20him%20out%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202021%2C%20there%20was%20a%20massive%2C%20unprecedented%20bird%20flu%20outbreak%20that%2C%20almost%20overnight%2C%20drove%20the%20price%20of%20egg%20products%20up%20in%20some%20cases%20500%25%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20I%20was%20only%20selling%20egg%20white-based%20protein%20powders%2C%20my%20profitable%20business%20essentially%20became%20unprofitable%20overnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20forced%20another%20pivot%3A%20He%20launched%20a%20vegan%2C%20chickpea-based%20protein%20powder%20that%20he%20no%20longer%20makes%2C%20but%20it%20introduced%20the%20idea%20of%20diversifying%20his%20product%20line.%20He%20now%20makes%20an%20almond-based%20vegan%20powder%20and%20a%20collagen-based%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20the%20challenges%2C%20we've%20adapted%2C%20we've%20iterated%2C%20and%20ultimately%20come%20out%20better%2C%20more%20resilient%2C%20more%20flexible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22067c1717-0564-42ba-8a49-d2753c5976d5%5C%22%3ELeaving%20education%20to%20run%20Drink%20Wholesome%20full-time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchrupp%20never%20imagined%20his%20life%20as%20a%20full-time%20entrepreneur%20running%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20this%20plan%20to%20teach%20for%20a%20while%20and%20then%20become%20an%20administrator%20and%20possibly%20even%20head%20of%20a%20school.%20That%20was%20a%20dream%20of%20mine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20juggling%20teaching%20and%20coaching%20with%20a%20growing%20business%20that%20was%20starting%20to%20feel%20more%20like%20a%20full-time%20job%20than%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20Schrupp%20had%20to%20decide%20between%20the%20two%20career%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20doing%20too%20much%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20wasn't%20doing%20anything%20well%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20as%20well%20as%20I%20could%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20discouraging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20just%20spread%20too%20thin.%20My%20life%20was%20very%20rich%20and%20rewarding%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20sleeping%20enough.%20I%20was%20very%20stressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22918%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Schrupp%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d38a07bb3f854015b6497%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESchrupp's%20sister%2C%20Tessa%2C%20joined%20Drink%20Wholesome%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jack%20Schrupp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20school%20year%2C%20he%20quit%20to%20run%20Drink%20Wholesome%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20wasn't%20challenging%20from%20a%20personal%20finance%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20spent%20five%20years%20teaching%20at%20boarding%20schools%20with%20free%20housing.%20I%20didn't%20earn%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20housing%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20cost%2C%20and%20I%20lived%20pretty%20modestly%2C%20I'd%20saved%20money%20and%20did%20certainly%20have%20a%20safety%20net%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20he%20could%20always%20go%20back%20to%20teaching%20if%20he%20needed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20trajectory%20of%20his%20company%2C%20which%20did%20seven%20figures%20in%20online%20sales%20in%202024%20according%20to%20screenshots%20of%20his%20sales%20dashboards%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20he%20won't%20need%20to%20return%20to%20a%20teaching%20career%20anytime%20soon%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20might%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20your%20own%20business%20is%20isolating%20and%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20a%20hard%20journey%2C%20which%20it%20often%20is%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20are%20doing%20it%20alone%20with%20no%20one%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20help%20or%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp%2C%20who%20works%20remotely%20from%20his%20home%20in%20Hanover%20and%20has%20one%20employee%3A%20his%20sister%2C%20who%20is%20based%20on%20the%20West%20Coast.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20that%20entrepreneurship%20is%20like%20a%20hack%20or%20should%20be%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20for%20everyone.%20You%20should%20definitely%2C%20if%20you're%20ever%20considering%20it%2C%20take%20into%20account%20the%20loneliness%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20being%20an%20entrepreneur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20perks%2C%20of%20course%20%E2%80%94%20he%20says%20he's%20earning%20more%20money%20as%20a%20business%20owner%20and%20remote%20work%20allows%20him%20to%20travel%20much%20more%20than%20his%20teaching%20career%20did%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he's%20figuring%20out%20if%20the%20money%20and%20flexibility%20are%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20so%20much%20that%20I'm%20lonely%2C%20but%20I'm%20professionally%20lonely.%20That's%20certainly%20the%20case%2C%20and%20I'm%20OK%20with%20it%20for%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schrupp.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20want%20to%20do%20this%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-former-teacher-bootstrapped-protein-powder-company-small-business-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738491421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d3764196626c4098606df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww