quot%3BThere's%20always%20someone%20hotter%20or%20taller%20or%20thinner%20or%20someone%20with%20a%20better%20job%2C%20or%20someone%20who%20holds%20their%20pen%20in%20a%20particular%20way%20so%20you%20don't%20get%20the%20ick%2C%26quot%3B%20Evans%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20we%20were%20only%20ever%20hooking%20up%2C%20the%20apps%20would%20always%20have%20you%20back%20in%20their%20pocket%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20lessons%20Evans%20has%20learned%20is%20for%20people%20to%20embrace%20dating%20outside%20their%20%26quot%3Btype.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20at%20exactly%20what%20that%20type%20is%2C%20it's%20often%20quite%20an%20outdated%20tick%20list%20of%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Evans%20said.%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20that%20we%20think%20we%20ought%20to%20like%20layered%20over%20time%20with%20our%2014-year-old%20teen%20crush%20on%20an%20American%20show%20doubled%20with%20a%20familiar%20face%20of%20an%20ex-boyfriend%20in%20university%20that%20it%20didn't%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20apps%20have%20led%20people%20to%20shut%20out%20people%20who%20they%20could%20have%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20relationship%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Evans%20said%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20didn't%20look%20exactly%20right%20on%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20they%20haven't%20fitted%20their%20rigid%2C%20on-paper%20litmus%20test%2C%20they%20haven't%20given%20it%20a%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20judging%20people%20so%20much%20on%20just%20a%20few%20words%20on%20a%20page.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20from%20a%20Bored%20Of%20Dating%20Apps%20singles%20mixer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678791668951662c9f203ab3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20BODA%20events%20are%20mixers%2C%20while%20others%20are%20held%20in%20bookshops.%3Cp%3EBored%20Of%20Dating%20Apps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22518093a1-0eb6-46b7-8e92-b064738f7e72%5C%22%3EFinding%20love%20and%20a%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20one%20golden%20rule%20anyone%20attending%20a%20BODA%20event%20must%20follow%3A%20ghosting%20is%20strictly%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20everyone%20to%20look%20after%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Evans%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20meet%20someone%20tonight%20and%20go%20on%20a%20date%20with%20them%2C%20please%20don't%20ghost%20them%20after.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvans%20said%20this%20basic%20rule%20of%20social%20interaction%20has%20been%20lost%20along%20the%20way%2C%20largely%20because%20of%20dating%20app%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffancy-first-date-no-connection-ghosted-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGhosting%20and%20standing%20people%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20the%20norm%2C%20with%20little%20consideration%20for%20someone's%20feelings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20cycle%20is%20particularly%20frustrating%20for%20people%20in%20their%2030s%20who%20may%20have%20friendship%20groups%20full%20of%20people%20settling%20down%2C%20getting%20married%2C%20and%20having%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvans%20felt%20this%20way%20herself.%20She%20felt%20isolated%20as%20her%20friends%20became%20more%20occupied%20with%20their%20own%20families%2C%20and%20spare%20cash%20once%20devoted%20to%20nights%20out%20with%20the%20girls%20was%20set%20aside%20for%20family%20holidays%20and%20living%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBODA%20gave%20Evans%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-free-lonely-so-we-started-walking-group-for-women-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocialize%20and%20find%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20situation%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20a%20community%20as%20well%20as%20a%20place%20to%20find%20love