20that%20this%20was%20%E2%80%94%2028%20nanometers%20%E2%80%94%20was%20going%20to%20be%20our%20tide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20TSMC's%2028-nanometer%20chips%20in%202011%20came%20at%20the%20perfect%20moment%2C%20Chang%20said%2C%20with%20the%20company%20poised%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20smartphone%20developers'%20growing%20need%20for%20semiconductor%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20Chang%20said%20he%20had%20thought%20for%20years%20about%20how%20to%20land%20Apple's%20business%2C%20the%20company%20had%20its%20own%20preferred%20way%20of%20doing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20is%20a%20very%20close-mouthed%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20try%20to%20talk%20to%20them%2C%20if%20you%20offer%2C%20you%20know%2C%20your%20service%2C%20they%20will%20just%20tell%20you%20to%20go%20away.%20They%20will%20come%20to%20see%20you%20when%20they%20are%20ready.%20That's%20what%20I%20knew%20about%20Apple%2C%20even%20then.%20And%20I%20know%20the%20same%20thing%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%2C%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20in%20the%20form%20of%20an%20unexpected%20dinner%20with%20Jeff%20Williams%2C%20Apple's%20operations%20boss%2C%20at%20Chang's%20own%20home.%20Chang%20said%20Williams%20got%20right%20to%20laying%20out%20the%20framework%20for%20a%20potential%20deal%20for%20TSMC%20to%20make%20iPhone%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFoundry%20our%20wafers%2C%20something%20like%20that.%20Pretty%20straightforward%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20recalled%20Williams%20telling%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20listened.%20That%20night%2C%20I%20think%20Jeff%20talked%20maybe%2080%25%20and%20I%20talked%2020%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20a%20twist%20%E2%80%94%20Apple%20wanted%20TSMC%20to%20produce%20a%2020-nanometer%20chip%2C%20which%20Chang%20viewed%20as%20a%20step%20back%20from%20the%2016-nanometer%20chip%20he%20viewed%20as%20the%20natural%20next%20step%20in%20TSMC's%20foundry%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20that%20was%20a%20surprise%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20frankly%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20disappointment%2C%20because%20the%20progression%20after%2028%20was%20going%20to%20be%2016.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20half%20step%20is%20a%20detour%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20founder%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFZItbr4ZJnc%3Fsi%3DeQknqleC6zOh79T9%26start%3D3127%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20offered%20TSMC%20a%2040%25%20gross%20margin%2C%20Chang%20said.%20The%20TSMC%20founder%20said%20he%20believed%20Apple%20was%20trying%20to%20be%20generous%20with%20the%20offer%2C%20but%20TSMC%20had%20already%20achieved%2045%25%20gross%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20said%20he%20kept%20quiet%20about%20that%20element%20of%20the%20proposal%2C%20deciding%20the%20dinner%20was%20not%20the%20right%20time%20to%20open%20up%20a%20negotiation%20over%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Chang%20said%20TSMC%20decided%20to%20produce%20only%20half%20of%20the%20supply%20of%20chips%20Apple%20was%20asking%20for.%20After%20relaying%20his%20offer%2C%20Chang%20said%20Williams%20called%20to%20put%20negotiations%20on%20pause%20while%20Apple%20entered%20into%20talks%20with%20Intel%2C%20who%20at%20the%20time%20made%20chips%20for%20Apple's%20Mac%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Chang%20said%20he%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Ball%20that%20worried%26quot%3B%20because%20he%20felt%20TSMC%20better%20fit%20the%20criteria%20that%20Apple%20was%20searching%20for%20in%20a%20supplier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20%E2%80%94%20at%20that%20time%20we%20thought%20we%20were%20almost%20at%20par%20with%20Intel%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlmost.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20at%20par%20with%20Intel.%20Manufacturing%2C%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20better%20than%20Intel.%20And%20customer%20trust%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20our%20customers%20trusted%20us%20more%20than%20Intel's%20customers%20trusted%20Intel.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Chang%20said%20he%20heard%20some%20good%20news%20from%20Tim%20Cook%20himself%20while%20getting%20lunch%20with%20him%20at%20Apple's%20cafeteria%20and%20carrying%20their%20food%20trays%20up%20to%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20there's%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20because%20Intel%20just%20does%20not%20know%20how%20to%20be%20a%20foundry%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20very%20short%20but%20very%20satisfactory%20answer%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20it%20was%20TSMC's%20reputation%20for%20addressing%20customers'%20every%20concern%20that%20gave%20it%20a%20leg%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Tim%20meant%20that%20the%20customer%20asks%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20learned%20to%20respond%20to%20every%20request.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20crazy%2C%20some%20of%20them%20were%20irrational%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20responded%20to%20each%20request%20courteously.%20Which%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20a%20lot%20of%20Intel's%20customer%20customers%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20you%20know%2C%20all%20the%20PC%20makers%20are%20Intel's%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20them%20liked%20Intel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIntel%20always%20acted%20like%20they%20were%20the%20only%20guy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel%20and%20Apple%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20prior%20to%20publication.%20A%20spokesperson%20fo