22CoreLogic%20weighed%20the%20cost%20of%20replacing%20homes%2C%20the%20frequency%20of%20climate%20disasters%2C%20and%20more%20to%20identify%20areas%20with%20lower%20risks%20from%20natural%20disasters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy%2CAlcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafest-cities-from-natural-disasters-for-us-homeowners-from-corelogic-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMust%20Understand%20Peculiarity%20Of%20Defence%20Budget%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20an%20exclusive%20post-Budget%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20said%20the%20government%20has%20not%20cut%20back%20on%20defence%20spending%2C%20rather%20it%20ensured%20that%20defence%20pensions%20and%20procurement%20expenses%20are%20never%20lowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pay%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20to%20them.%20This%20time%20also%20there%20was%20no%20issue%20in%20the%20defence%20budget.%20But%20we%20must%20understand%20the%20peculiarity%20of%20the%20defence%20budget.%20The%20year%20in%20which%20the%20payment%20has%20to%20be%20made%2C%20that%20year%20a%20higher%20provisioning%20has%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20year%20the%20order%20is%20placed%2C%20it%20is%20the%20instalment%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20paid.%20The%20payments%20spread%20over%20a%20long%20term...%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20and%20we%20should%20recognise%20the%20fact%20that%20nearly%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20components%20made%20in%20India%20are%20bought%20by%20defence%20units%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20a%20different%20matter%20if%20a%20large-ticket%20purchase%20has%20to%20be%20made%20from%20another%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMainly%2C%20running%20consumables%20and%20other%20things%20are%20bought%20from%20India.%20We%20make%20defence%20components%20not%20only%20for%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20we%20also%20export%20them.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20crossed%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20earnings%20with%20defence%20components%20exports%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Budget%202025%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20set%20aside%20Rs%206.81%20lakh%20crore%20crore%20as%20the%20defence%20budget%20for%20fiscal%202026%2C%20a%209.53%20per%20cent%20increase%20over%20the%20allocation%20of%20Rs%206.22%20lakh%20crore%20for%20the%20current%20fiscal.%20The%20armed%20forces%20have%20been%20looking%20to%20acquire%20new%20weapon%20systems%20in%20the%20face%20of%20security%20challenges%20from%20China%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%2C%20Rs%201.8%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20capital%20expenditure%20that%20largely%20includes%20purchasing%20weapons%2C%20aircraft%2C%20warships%20and%20other%20military%20hardware.%20The%20budget%20for%20defence%20is%20around%201.9%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20projected%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20allocation%20is%20around%206.2%20per%20cent%20if%20compared%20to%20the%20revised%20allocation%20of%20Rs%206.41%20lakh%20crore%20for%20the%20current%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738488780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fe8s79od_nirmala-_625x300_02_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fmust-understand-peculiarity-of-defence-budget-says-nirmala-sitharaman-on-budget-2025-7616384%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20an%20exclusive%20post-Budget%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20said%20the%20government%20has%20not%20cut%20back%20on%20defence%20spending%2C%20rather%20it%20ensured%20that%20defence%20pensions%20and%20procurement%20expenses%20are%20never%20lowered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano