rt%20the%20production%20of%20Makhana%20in%20north%20Bihar.%20She%20also%20said%20greenfield%20airports%20will%20be%20developed%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Budget%20also%20announced%20financial%20help%20for%20the%20Western%20Kosi%20Canal%20project%20in%20Mithilanchal%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20boost%20irrigation.%20It%20also%20announced%20a%20plan%20for%20IIT%20Patna's%20expansion%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20National%20Institute%20of%20Food%20Technology%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20this%20Budget%20was%20prepared%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20Bihar%20and%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20this%20was%20a%20budget%20for%20the%20people.%20She%20then%20quoted%20the%20timeless%20phrase%20of%20former%20US%20President%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20and%20said%20this%20was%20a%20budget%20%26quot%3Bof%20the%20people%2C%20by%20the%20people%2C%20for%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20characteristic%20changes%20in%20this%20Budget%20are%20based%20on%20people's%20voices.%20The%20Opposition%20parties%20always%20feel%20the%20Budget%20is%20for%20the%20election.%20I%20disagree.%20Are%20their%20elections%20in%20Assam%20too%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20announcement%20for%20a%20urea%20plant%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20Bihar%20is%20densely%20populated%20and%20has%20cultural%20centres%20such%20as%20Nalanda%20and%20Rajgir.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20this%2C%20there%20is%20no%20good%20international%20airport.%20Aren't%20we%20all%20responsible%20for%20this%3F%20Shouldn't%20we%20give%20it%20to%20them%3F%20Someone%20asked%2C%20'can%20you%20only%20see%20Bihar%3F'.%20Isn't%20Bihar%20a%20part%20of%20India%3F%20Bihar's%20workers%20are%20found%20across%20the%20country.%20Shouldn't%20there%20be%20work%20in%20their%20villages%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20welcomed%20the%20Budget%20announcem