s%20have%20worked%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%20works%20when%20he%20wants%20for%20a%20local%20retail%20store%20that%20gives%20him%20the%2020%25%20more%20income%20he%20needs%20to%20live%20comfortably.%20He%20said%20working%20as%20a%20cashier%20lets%20him%20interact%20with%20new%20people%20and%20have%20a%20purpose%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20plan%20on%20retiring%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20the%20type%20of%20person%20who's%20going%20to%20go%20out%20and%20play%20golf%20every%20day%20or%20hang%20out%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20that%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Rice%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20always%20hear%20about%20people%20who%20say%20they're%20retired%20and%20don't%20do%20anything%2C%20and%20then%20years%20later%2C%20they%20pass%20away%20because%20they're%20not%20keeping%20their%20minds%20active.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-planning-regrets-older-americans-millionaire-frugal-living-social-security-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738487401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6780442588b000981b4a48f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-planning-regrets-older-americans-millionaire-frugal-living-social-security-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Older%20Americans%20with%20few%20regrets%20about%20planning%20for%20retirement%20shared%20their%20strategies%20for%20achieving%20success%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20not%20millionaires.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40businessinsider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-planning-regrets-older-americans-millionaire-frugal-living-social-security-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20rolls%20out%20his%20