2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20states%20still%20largely%20controlling%20funding%20and%20public%20school%20curricula%2C%20though%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20Trump's%20plans%20to%20shape%20education%20across%20all%20classrooms%20would%20be%20implemented%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20would%20likely%20face%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20executive%20orders%20addressed%20examining%20the%20redirection%20of%20funds%20toward%20K-12%20schools%20that%20prioritize%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Fending-radical-indoctrination-in-k-12-schooling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatriotic%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20removing%20%26quot%3Bgender%20ideology%26quot%3B%20from%20classrooms%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Fexpanding-educational-freedom-and-opportunity-for-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpanding%20school%20choice%3C%2Fa%3E%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJon%20Valant%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Brown%20Center%20on%20Education%20Policy%20at%20The%20Brookings%20Institution%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20executive%20orders%20alone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bdon't%20actually%20do%20all%20that%20much.%26quot%3B%20Rather%2C%20they%20direct%20federal%20agencies%20to%20prepare%20guidance%20that%20would%20determine%20how%20the%20orders%20will%20be%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20Valant%20said%20they%20could%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20chilling%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20prompting%20some%20schools%2C%20districts%2C%20and%20states%20to%20obey%20Trump's%20wishes%20to%20avoid%20any%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20may%20interpret%20them%20as%20having%20more%20bite%20than%20they%20actually%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265fbd136-ea8a-49c0-9db6-f06b41e132df%5C%22%3EUncertainty%20over%20a%20federal%20role%20in%20school%20choice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20schools%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20guidance%20from%20federal%20agencies%20on%20how%20to%20carry%20out%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%2C%20the%20orders%20themselves%20appear%20to%20have%20contradictions%2C%20Jonathan%20Zimmerman%2C%20an%20education%20policy%20historian%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20on%20reshaping%20public%20school%20curricula%20is%20entitled%20%26quot%3Bending%20radical%20indoctrination%20in%20K-12%20schooling%2C%26quot%3B%20going%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20order%20will%20%26quot%3Bpromote%20patriotic%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20anti-indoctrination%20order%20is%20itself%20an%20indoctrination%20order%2C%20which%20is%20trying%20to%20determine%20what%20everybody%20can%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimmerman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20area%20of%20uncertainty%20is%20the%20legality%20of%20Trump's%20attempt%20to%20expand%20school%20choice%2C%20a%20system%20that%20provides%20parents%20with%20state-%20or%20federally%20funded%20vouchers%20to%20send%20their%20kids%20to%20a%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20calls%20for%20the%20education%20secretary%20to%20issue%20guidance%20on%20how%20states%20can%20use%20federal%20funds%20for%20alternative%20education%20like%20private%20school%20vouchers.%20It%20also%20calls%20for%20an%20examination%20of%20how%20states%20could%20use%20federal%20block%20grants%20to%20expand%20school%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20school%20choice%20lauded%20the%20executive%20order.%20Robert%20Enlow%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20EdChoice%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fedchoice%2Fstatus%2F1884675891789234225%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20crucial%20step%20toward%20empowering%20parents%20and%20giving%20them%20greater%20control%20over%20their%20children's%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Randi%20Weingarten%2C%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Teachers%20which%20opposes%20school%20choice%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20executive%20order%20%26quot%3Bdiminishes%20community%20schools%20and%20the%20services%20they%20provide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20order%20hijacks%20federal%20money%20used%20to%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20poor%20and%20disadvantaged%20kids%20and%20hands%20it%20directly%20to%20unaccountable%20private%20operators%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20private%20school%20vouchers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-school-vouchers-arizona-cautionary-tale-savings-accounts-parents-cash-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20surged%20over%20the%20past%20decade%3C%2Fa%3E.%20States%20like%20Ohio%20and%20Arkansas%20have%20expanded%20their%20voucher%20programs%20to%20allow%20most%20parents%20to%20receive%20funding%20to%20send%20their%20kids%20to%20private%20schools%2C%20and%20Arizona%20was%20the%20first%20state%20to%20create%20a%20universal%20voucher%20program%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValant%20said%20that%20while%20many%20Republican%20states%20support%20school%20choice%2C%20Republican%20lawmakers%20value%20local%20control%2C%20and%20they%20might%20not%20support%20a%20federal%20hand%20in%20state%20education%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20Valant%20said%20he's%20skeptical%20that%20the%20administration%20will%20actually%20end%20up%20making%20big%20moves%20on%20that%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20challenges%20to%20the%20executive%20orders%20are%20also%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20gray%20area%20in%20all%20of%20this%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20a%20world%20where%20there%20aren't%20some%20court%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimmerman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20clear%20what%20their%20legal%20authority%20is.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20that's%20a%20recipe%20for%20a%20legal%20challenge%20when%20you%20don't%20really%20know%20where%20the%20legal%20authority%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-school-choice-vouchers-education-policy-exeuctive-orders-anti-woke-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738487221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d4750bfebcc4d029d6fe6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-school-choice-vouchers-education-policy-exeuctive-orders-anti-woke-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Trump%20issued%20two%20executive%20orders%20that%20call%20on%20his%20administration%20to%20look%20into%20more%20funding%20for%20schools%20that%20adopt%20his%20political%20ideologies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-school-choice-vouchers-education-policy-exeuctive-orders-anti-woke-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGives%20Me%20Gratification%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20Tells%20NDTV%20Her%20Favourite%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20with%20NDTV%2C%20%C2%A0expressed%20strong%20personal%20satisfaction%20with%20a%20key%20initiative%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%3A%20transforming%20India%20Post%20into%20a%20major%20logistics%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20first%20interview%20after%20presenting%20the%20budget%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20was%20asked%20by%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20about%20the%