0internet%20jokes%2C%20cutesy%20animals%2C%20and%20pop%20culture%20fads%2C%20meme%20coins%20have%20been%20in%20circulation%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20While%20the%20tokens%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftruth-about-crypto-bitcoin-replace-money-us-dollar-banks-gambling-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20value%20as%20currency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20price%20can%20soar%20upon%20release%2C%20as%20speculators%20jump%20on%20the%20new%20offering.%20That%20allows%20insiders%20who%20held%20the%20coins%20before%20their%20public%20debut%20to%20turn%20a%20quick%20profit%2C%20with%20some%20top%20tokens%20achieving%20multibillion-dollar%20valuations%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes.%20But%20the%20coins%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20crash%20just%20as%20quickly%2C%20leaving%20latecomers%20with%20steep%20losses.%20Emboldened%20by%20Jenner's%20move%2C%20a%20host%20of%20other%20B-list%20celebrities%20rushed%20to%20mint%20their%20own%20cyber%20tokens%3A%20the%20boxer%20Floyd%20Mayweather%20Jr.%2C%20the%20Nigerian%20singer%20Davido%2C%20the%20influencer%20Andrew%20Tate.%20Even%20the%20president%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20gotten%20in%20on%20the%20act%2C%20issuing%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-launches-cryptocurrency-days-before-inauguration-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24Trump%20and%20%24Melania%20coins%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20site%20where%20Jenner%20released%20her%20token%2C%20Pump.fun%2C%20is%20now%20the%20leading%20generator%20of%20meme%20coins%2C%20with%20over%203%20million%20registered%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20pop%20culture%20officially%20adopts%20a%20new%20technology%2C%20it's%20a%20wrap%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Joe%20McCann%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Asymmetric%20Financial%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20cryptocurrency%20firms%20to%20take%20a%20major%20stake%20in%20meme%20coins.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20basically%20cemented%20as%20a%20thing%20that%20is%20not%2