ebrity%20tokens%20released%20that%20month%20%E2%80%94%20two%20from%20the%20rappers%20Rich%20the%20Kid%20and%20Soulja%20Boy%2C%20and%20two%20from%20the%20models%20Kazumi%20and%20Ivana%20Kn%C3%B6ll.%20That%20suggested%20the%20same%20person%20was%20running%20the%20launch%20for%20each%20of%20the%20coins%20%E2%80%94%20that%20a%20single%20mastermind%20was%20behind%20the%20pump%20and%20dumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20second%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20the%20tokens%20they're%20launching%20are%20full%20of%20crap%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaiman%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20can%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20insider%20activity%2C%20because%20all%20of%20the%20holders%20are%20connected%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20clear%20indicator%20that%20the%20people%20launching%20the%20coin%20actually%20own%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20supply%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20outrage%20and%20confusion%20about%20her%20coin%20spread%2C%20Jenner%20found%20herself%20racing%20to%20do%20damage%20control.%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20not%20been%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tweeted%20two%20hours%20after%20releasing%20%24Jenner.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20out%20on%20the%20golf%20course.%26quot%3B%20She%20included%20a%20video%20from%20her%20manager%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsophia-hutchins-comments-on-caitlyn-jenner-relationship-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophia%20Hutchins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20wearing%20a%20blue%20windbreaker%20and%20a%20peach%20hairband.%20%26quot%3BYou%20guys%2C%26quot%3B%20Hutchins%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bher%20account%20has%20not%20been%20hacked.%20You%20can%20rest%20assured%20her%20crypto%20is%20definitely%20performing%20extraordinarily%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20assurances%2C%20it%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20Jenner's%20coin%20to%20tank.%20Within%20days%2C%20after%20peaking%20at%20a%20market%20cap%20north%20of%20%2446%20million%2C%20it%20plunged%