h%20Vaiman%20showing%20that%20he%20had%20owned%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehalf%20the%20supply%20of%20%24Jason%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20dumped%20it%20minutes%20after%20Derulo%20promoted%20the%20coin%2C%20pocketing%20a%20cool%20%24180%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Derulo%20throws%20his%20hands%20in%20the%20air%20as%20he%20performs%20on%20stage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679900667bb3f854015aa07a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Derulo%20promised%20he'd%20never%20sell%20his%20coin%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Arora%20shared%20evidence%20that%20he%20took%20part%20in%20a%20pump%20and%20dump.%3Cp%3EOmar%20Vega%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20iHeartRadio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVaiman%20was%20confused.%20It%20made%20no%20sense%20that%20Arora%20would%20turn%20over%20evidence%20that%20implicated%20himself%20so%20clearly.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20this%20guy%20just%20committing%20everything%20to%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20Vaiman%20wondered.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20point%3F%20He%20is%20surrendering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20doing%20more%20than%20that.%20Arora%20shared%20another%20address%20for%20a%20wallet%20%E2%80%94%20one%20he%20said%20belonged%20to%20Derulo.%20Vaiman%20could%20see%20that%20the%20wallet%20had%20received%20%24Jason%20tokens%20directly%20from%20Arora%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20turned%20around%20and%20dumped%20%2420%2C000%20in%20coins%2C%20not%20long%20after%20Derulo%20had%20promised%20he%20would%20%26quot%3BNEVER%20SELL.%26quot%3B%20The%20evidence%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20Derulo%20himself%20was%20complicit%20in%20the%20crypto%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJason%20Derulo%20was%20actually%20selling%20behind%20his%20community's%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaiman%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20big%20piece%20of%20evidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20was%20more.%20To%20Vai