ets-to-defend-u19-womens-t20-world-cup-title%2Farticleshow%2F117854827.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Customs%20Benefit%20To%20Tesla%2C%20Harley%20To%20Counter%20Trump%20Tariff%3F%20N%20Sitharaman%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20introduced%20custom%20duty%20rationalisation%20to%20ensure%20the%20Indian%20economy%20becomes%20%3Cem%3Eaatmanirbhar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(self-reliant).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20was%20responding%20to%20NDTV's%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20on%20whether%20the%20budgetary%20announcement%20of%20reducing%20custom%20duty%20for%20many%20automobiles%2C%20which%20will%20benefit%20companies%20like%20Tesla%20and%20Harley%20Davidson%2C%20is%20a%20signal%20amid%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20announcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20at%20our%20own%20economy.%20We%20are%20looking%20strengthen%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20to%20make%20it%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20added%20that%20the%20Union%20Budget's%20announcement%20of%20reducing%20custom%20duty%20aims%20at%20making%20cheap%20raw%20materials%20available%20for%20MSMEs%2C%20getting%20critical%20minerals%20and%20allowing%20Indian%20companies%20to%20import%20materials%20and%20export%20a%20finished%20product%20of%20high%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETariffs%20on%20Harley%20Davidson%20bikes%20were%20slashed%20further%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20proposed%20US%20visit.%20For%20motorcycles%20with%20engine%20capacity%20not%20exceeding%201600%20cc%2C%20the%20duty%20on%20CBUs%20(Completely%20Built%20Up)%20has%20been%20slashed%20from%2050%20per%20cent%20to%2040%20per%20cent.%20For%20larger%20motorcycles%20with%20engine%20capacity%20exceeding%201600%20cc%2C%20the%20reductions%20are%20higher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20basic%20customs%20duty%20on%20the%20import%20of%20cars%20and%20other%20motor%20vehicles%20has%20also%20been%20reduced%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20their%20effective%20duty%20rates%20will%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20said%20the%20government%20has%20created%20a%20balance%20between%20strengthening%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20and%20equally%20focusing%20on%20key%20sectors%20like%20health%2C%20nutrition%20and%20education%20through%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20rejected%20criticism%20by%20the%20Opposition%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20was%20only%20trying%20to%20woo%20voters%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Delhi%20through%20the%20announcements%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20presented%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025-26%2C%20her%20eighth%20consecutive%20presentation%2C%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738486140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fo87othoo_nirmala-sitharaman_625x300_02_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Freduced-custom-duty-to-counter-trumps-tariff-spree-nirmala-sitharamans-response-7615879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20introduced%20custom%20duty%20rationalisation%20to%20ensure%20the%20Indian%20economy%20becomes%20aatmanirbhar%20(self-reliant).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Freduced-custom-duty-to-counter-trumps-tariff-spree-nirmala-sitharamans-response-7615879%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%20Win%20For%20Gig%20Workers%3A%20Free%20Treatment%20Up%20To%20Rs%205%20Lakh%2C%20N%20Sitharaman%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20Union%20Budget's%20provisions%20will%20allow%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20free%20t