ys-the-actor-after-55-kilos-weight-drop%2Farticleshow%2F117851531.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BModi%20Government%20Recognised%20Honest%20Taxpayers%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20Exclusive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20aim%20in%20this%20Budget%20was%20to%20extend%20support%20to%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today%2C%20the%20day%20after%20presenting%20the%20Budget%20in%20Parliament%20and%20announcing%20major%20tax%20reliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20is%20to%20increase%20consumption.%20The%20government%20always%20recognised%20honest%20taxpayers.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20provide%20support%20to%20the%20middle%20class.%20Those%20earning%20Rs%201%20lakh%20need%20tax%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20told%20NDTV's%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20in%20her%20first%20interview%20after%20presenting%20the%20Budget%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20eighth%20consecutive%20Budget%20speech%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20announced%20that%20salaried%20individuals%20with%20annual%20income%20up%20to%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20won't%20need%20to%20pay%20income%20tax%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%20She%20also%20revised%20tax%20slabs%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%20Under%20the%20revised%20slabs%2C%20tax%20on%20income%20up%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh%20is%20nil.%20Income%20between%20Rs%204%20and%20Rs%208%20lakh%20will%20be%20taxed%20at%20five%20per%20cent.%20Between%20Rs%208%20and%20Rs%2012%20lakh%2C%20it%20will%20be%2010%20per%20cent.%20Between%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2016%20lakh%2C%20it%20will%20be%2015%20per%20cent.%20The%20tax%20rate%20between%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20will%20be%2020%20per%20cent.%20Between%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2024%20lakh%2C%20it%20will%20be%2025%20per%20cent.%20And%20income%20above%20Rs%2024%20lakh%20will%20be%20taxed%20at%2030%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20reduce%20the%20tax%20burden%20on%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20leave%20more%20money%20in%20their%20hands%26quot%3B.%20It%20will%20also%20boost%20household%20consumption%2C%20savings%2C%20and%20investment%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Budget%20document%2C%20the%20government%20will%20provide%20rebates%20to%20those%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%20For%20salaried%20individuals%2C%20this%20ceiling%20will%20be%20Rs%2012.75%20lakh%2C%20including%20the%20standard%20deduction%20of%20Rs%2075%2C000.%20The%20Budget%20document%20has%20a%20table%20illustrating%20the%20rebates%2C%20starting%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20and%20rising%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20for%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20document%20has%20specified%20that%20new%20tax%20rates%20and%20the%20breather%20for%20those%20earning%20up%20to%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20a%20year%20are%20applicable%20only%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20introduced%20in%202020.%C2%A0This%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20government's%20push%20for%20this%20new%20regime%20that%20aims%20to%20simplify%20personal%20tax%20by%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20complications%20of%20exemptions.%C2%A0In%20a%20press%20interaction%20last%20evening%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20clarified%20that%20the%20old%20regime%20has%20not%20been%20discontinued.%20Top%20government%20officials%20said%20nearly%2075%20per%20cent%20taxpayers%20had%20already%20moved%20to%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20the%20Budget%20reflects%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20fulfilling%20the%20aspirations%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians.%20He%20said%20this%20Budget%20would%20add%20momentum%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bcollective%20resolve%20of%20building%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%3C%