en%20the%20voice%20of%20Japan's%20bullet%20train%20for%2020%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Donna%20Burke%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDonna%20Burke%2C%2060%2C%20started%20her%20teaching%20career%20in%20Perth%2C%20Australia%2C%20but%20harbored%20deeper%20ambitions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20left%20the%20profession%20to%20follow%20her%20dream%20of%20being%20a%20famous%20singer%20and%20actor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20she's%20a%20professional%20singer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20voice%20of%20Japan's%20bullet%20train.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3EDonna%20Burke%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20actually%20got%20my%20education%20at%20a%20teacher%20training%20college%20completely%20for%20free.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-calls-australian-government-fascists-over-misinformation-bill-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAustralian%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20paid%20for%20you%20to%20attend%20university%20if%20you%20worked%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years.%20I%20stayed%20in%20a%20banking%20job%20for%20exactly%20two%20years%20and%20two%20days%20so%20I%20could%20claim%20free%20higher%20education%20and%20retrain%20as%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents%20didn't%20encourage%20my%20true%20aspirations%20%E2%80%94%20singing%20and%20acting%20%E2%80%94%20but%20saw%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-teaching-to-become-journalist-it-was-a-bad-idea-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eteaching%20as%20a%20safe%20career%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20which%20I%20could%20always%20fall%20back.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20seven%20children%2C%20and%20we%20were%20encouraged%20to%20do%20everything%20we%20could%20to%20be%20financially%20stable.%20Two%20of%20my%20older%20sisters%20also%20went%20into%20teacher%20training.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20reflect%20now%20on%20whether%20it%20was%20good%20advice%20to%20put%20my%20dreams%20second.%20Perhaps%20it%20was.%20I%20later%20really%20wanted%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-moving-to-japan-westerner-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emove%20to%20Japan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20now%20live%20%E2%80%94%20to%20work.%20One%20of%20the%20visa%20requirements%20was%20that%20you%20have%20a%20university%20degree.%20Without%20following%20my%20parents'%20advice%2C%20I'd%20have%20been%20ineligible.%20But%20now%20I%20get%20to%20do%20something%20I%20truly%20love.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7a2c0e5-614a-4c71-b97b-585dac5657a4%5C%22%3EI%20never%20thought%20teaching%20would%20be%20a%20job%20for%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20began%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-teaching-big-tech-salary-growth-mental-health-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20teaching%20career%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20returning%20to%20work%20at%20the%20same%20school%20I'd%20attended%20as%20a%20student.%20The%20boys%20in%20my%20class%20were%20an%20absolute%20nightmare%20and%20the%20girls%20barely%20got%20my%20attention%20as%20I%20was%20so%20busy%20trying%20to%20calm%20and%20control%20the%20unruly%20boys.%20I%20followed%20the%20common%20advice%20on%20winning%20obedience%20as%20a%20teacher%3A%20don't%20crack%20a%20smile%20before%20Easter.%20I%20was%20super%20strict%3B%20I%20had%20to%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20moved%20on%20to%20teach%20older%20students%20Religion%2C%20English%2C%20and%20Drama%20at%20a%20different%20high%20school.%20It%20was%20heaven%3B%20I%20could%20relax%20and%20crack%20jokes%20without%20losing%20control%20of%20the%20class.%20They'd%20barely%20laugh%2C%20though.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20never%20hoped%20it'd%20be%20a%20job%20for%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-who-were-almost-cast-in-tv-shows-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wanted%20to%20be%20onstage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20teaching%20is%20like%20being%20onstage%3B%20it's%20like%20acting.%20You%20have%20to%20pretend%20you%20don't%20care%20when%20you%20deeply%20care.%20You%20have%20to%20stifle%20laughter%2C%20keep%20a%20straight%20face%2C%20act%20really%20disappointed%2C%20or%20say%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Wow%2C%20that's%20amazing!%26quot%3B%20knowing%20that%2030%20young%20adults%20are%20watching%20your%20every%20move.%20But%20they%20don't%20want%20a%20performer%3B%20they%20want%20a%20teacher.%20I%20never%20said%20it%20out%20loud%2C%20but%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20settling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ff0fc5e-a452-4686-b004-2117b0ee6180%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20moved%20to%20Tokyo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20eight%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-tourists-make-in-perth-australia-travel-tips-american-expat-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyears%20of%20teaching%20in%20Perth%2C%20Australia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20ad%20for%20a%20teaching%20job%20in%20Tokyo.%20At%20the%20interview%2C%20they%20said%20the%20job%20involved%20less%20teaching%20and%20more%20helping%20Japanese%20young%20people%20with%20their%20English%20conversation%20skills.%20It%20felt%20like%20an%20opportunity%20for%20a%20role%20with%20fewer%20responsibilities%20in%